{"tid":568781,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【BLEACH死神】福士蒼汰新預告現學生造型　代理死神滅惡靈唔貶眼","createTime":"2018-02-22T06:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T13:35:08.000Z","uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"777bc280c7b2918373d88c6bb6995356916ecfff","tid":568781,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:16:52.000Z","msg":"日本漫改電影《BLEACH死神》（港譯：漂靈）2016年已宣布真人化，不過一直對電影消息相當密實，連過去公開的劇照和預告片，主角福士蒼汰不是以背面或側面示人，就是埋在陰影中。而在今日發布的新預告中，觀眾終於可以見到黑崎一護的完整造型，雖然電影的選角在漫畫迷間評價麻麻，但驚喜的是「惡靈」CG反而不錯，可以睇定啲先喎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1223696/xlarge/9c4cbddbae9391c93b40d8197318b868.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1223696%2Fxlarge%2F9c4cbddbae9391c93b40d8197318b868.jpg&h=279bcaa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Bleach死神》起用杉咲花同福士蒼汰嘅配搭似乎唔多受歡迎。（劇照）<br />\n《BLEACH死神》新預告公開了多個新畫面，除了早前出現過的巨形斬魄刀，還有「死神」朽木露琪亞在黑崎一護家中出現、二人對上惡靈和即將化為代理死神進行戰鬥和消滅虛的情節，還原度算相當不錯，只是角色造型依然爭咁啲。特別是由20歲新生代演技派女星杉咲花飾演露琪亞，最初公開定裝時已被指完全認不出是同一角色，在片中雖然只有短短幾個鏡頭，仍能隱約看到跟露琪亞幾乎判若兩人，說是全新角色也有人會相信，相比之下，24歲的福士蒼汰再演高中生的違和感即時減弱。<br />\n<br />\n漫畫原著講述主角黑崎一護是個普通人類，由於母親遺傳自小就能看見幽靈，一日，死神露琪亞為消滅稱為「虛」的惡靈，誤闖黑崎家，意外發現他竟能看見並碰觸到自己，其後黑崎家人遭惡靈攻擊，露琪亞為保護黑崎一家在戰鬥中受傷，不得已下把死神靈力借給一護，最終成功擊退虛，能力盡失的露琪亞只好寄住黑崎家，而黑崎則要暫時接手死神的任務。真人電影由《GANTZ殺戮都市》和《死亡筆記：照亮新世紀》導演佐藤信介執導，估計將會覆蓋漫畫第1至8卷的故事，預計7月20日在日本上映。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/X5pB0IQZyuM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FX5pB0IQZyuM&d=3yCpOMOjuSI16DLlVAJxx%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9c6c8ebe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/X5pB0IQZyuM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/161644/-BLEACH%E6%AD%BB%E7%A5%9E-%E7%A6%8F%E5%A3%AB%E8%92%BC%E6%B1%B0%E6%96%B0%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%E7%8F%BE%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B-%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E6%AD%BB%E7%A5%9E%E6%BB%85%E6%83%A1%E9%9D%88%E5%94%94%E8%B2%B6%E7%9C%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F161644%2F-BLEACH%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E7%25A5%259E-%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%2592%25BC%25E6%25B1%25B0%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25A0%2590%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%259E%258B-%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E7%25A5%259E%25E6%25BB%2585%25E6%2583%25A1%25E9%259D%2588%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25B2%25B6%25E7%259C%25BC&d=3yCpOMOjuSI16DLlVAJxx%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6c116ee8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/161644/-BLEACH%E6%AD%BB%E7%A5%9E-%E7%A6%8F%E5%A3%AB%E8%92%BC%E6%B1%B0%E6%96%B0%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%E7%8F%BE%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B-%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E6%AD%BB%E7%A5%9E%E6%BB%85%E6%83%A1%E9%9D%88%E5%94%94%E8%B2%B6%E7%9C%BC</a>"},{"pid":"0e1cec26c721d163a548acb20906087a07851318","tid":568781,"uid":38528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"隻虛CG得唔錯,但屌你老味露棋亞個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw拿拿林出血戰動畫啦屌,想J D卍解呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c49e28bff6cb208836e1882c2a3fcacb0c6c1b","tid":568781,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"隻露其亞真係做乜撚野<br />\n<br />\n好撚唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909f8fcdceec21fdf0da397e9b63148905fbfa82","tid":568781,"uid":82558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:44:41.000Z","msg":"得第一卷至第八卷，有咩好睇"},{"pid":"63d4f88b85d1c6b9987981a5347b430ee64f9246","tid":568781,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0e1cec26c721d163a548acb20906087a07851318","tid":568781,"uid":38528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"隻虛CG得唔錯,但屌你老味露棋亞個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw拿拿林出血戰動畫啦屌,想J D卍解呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:53:01.000Z","msg":"血戰出黎做乜<br />\n<br />\n垃圾劇情垃圾結局 <br />\n<br />\n邊有公司想自己蝕錢"},{"pid":"5cd34ec50ed3ca9b5de0d733421b28e1c00bf4c4","tid":568781,"uid":41524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"條女有冇再柒啲"},{"pid":"c384378afda7e5c90c6e5d5f9763f29275a90fbc","tid":568781,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"露琪亞: Nobody knows who i really am"},{"pid":"fdc29dfb8b0c96643a0a91cffcf1afa3e48b4a20","tid":568781,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c384378afda7e5c90c6e5d5f9763f29275a90fbc","tid":568781,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"露琪亞: Nobody knows who i really am"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"Life is like a boat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d83b6f59ea1d062913247fa2310a34b58bce16","tid":568781,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"... 睇完預告 吸引力極為不大"}]}